# Contact / Request Demo form — email delivery.
#
# The form posts to /api/contact, which emails submissions to
# hello@persimmon-care.com. Configure ONE provider below.
#
# Option A — Web3Forms (no account needed, recommended):
#   1. Go to https://web3forms.com, enter hello@persimmon-care.com, and
#      click the verification link they email you.
#   2. Paste your Access Key here.
WEB3FORMS_ACCESS_KEY=

# Option B — Formspree (free account). Create a form pointed at
# hello@persimmon-care.com and paste its endpoint URL.
# FORMSPREE_ENDPOINT=https://formspree.io/f/xxxxxxx
